    Buying an apartment in Tellapur: Property market insights

    Tellapur is one of the popular localities in the city to buy an apartment in Hyderabad. Some of the popular societies for buying an apartment in Tellapur are My Home Tridasa, My Home Sayuk and Aliens Space Station. These are the most preferred societies in Tellapur, known for their livability, quality and location. Around 462 apartments are available for sale out of which 239 apartments are ready to move while 223 apartments are currently under-construction.

    How good is Tellapur in terms of connectivity?

    Tellapur has several transit points in proximity which ensures its inter-connectivity to nearby areas. Telapur railway station, Bhel railway station, Lingampally, etc, are crucial for Tellapur connectivity.

    How is Tellapur neighborhood?

    As far as social infrastructure is concerned, there are 22 educational institutes near Tellapur such as Pavithra International School, Triveni Talent Schools, Centeral Grass Court, Science Complex, Epistemo Vikas Leadership School and Kidzee Pre-School etc. For medical needs, some of the nearby hospitals are American Oncology Institute, Citizens Specialty Hospital, etc. Most of the societies in Tellapur has amenities such as Parking, Club house and Lift, etc. Tellapur has few new projects as well which are launched recently. This includes Deepti Chs ltd.
    To read more about the positives and negatives of Tellapur, see here.

    Price Trends for apartments in Tellapur

    Currently, the apartment prices in Tellapur hover around ₹ 8200 per sq ft. That means, the average property price for a regular 2 bhk apartment in Tellapur costs around ₹ 73.8 lakh, a 3 bhk apartment in Tellapur costs around ₹ 98.4 lakh and a 1 bhk apartment in Tellapur costs around ₹ 49.2 lakh.
    If you are an end -user or an investor looking for rental returns, Tellapur offers 239 ready apartments, which are available on an immediate basis.
